2112.subject: ASAP
2112.descrlong: Provides supplemental support for Japanese Language (JAPN) courses.  Students work in small groups with a tutor from the Academic Skills Achievement Program (ASAP) and receive assistance on course assignments and study skills.  Groups meet one hour per week.  Credit/ no credit only.
